BEGIN_PGML

Tonya crashes into Nancy while they are practicing their figure skating routines. Tonya's mass is [`[$mt]`] [`kg`] and Nancy's mass is [`[$mn]`] [`kg`]. Just before the collision occurs, Tonya's velocity is [`[$vt]`] [`m/s`] and Nancy's velocity is [`[$vn]`] [`m/s`]. During the collision, Tonya exerts an average force of [`[$f]`] [`N`] against Nancy.

*a)* How big is the average force Nancy exerts against Tonya during the collision?

[`F=`] [_____]{"$f"} [`N`]  

*b)* If this is the only horizontal force acting on each skater during the collision, what average horizontal acceleration does each skater experience during the collision?

[`a_T=`] [_____]{"$at"} [`m/s^2`]  
[`a_N=`] [_____]{"$an"} [`m/s^2`]  

*c)* If the collision is perfectly inelastic, how fast will Tonya and Nancy be moving immediately after the collision?

[`v=`] [_____]{"$v"} [`m/s`]  

END_PGML

